---
title: Steakhouse-Style Pork Chops with Creamy Sauce
description: Why reserve Montreal steak spice for beef when its zesty flavour is so delicious? Mustard, onion, garlic and peppercorns combine in a delicious spice blend that pairs perfectly with pork.

